## Adjusting the Method

The exponent **4/5** can be tuned:
- If FWER > 0.07 → increase exponent toward 1 (approaches Holm-Bonferroni)
- If FWER < 0.03 → decrease exponent toward 3/4 (more lenient, higher power)

